<template>
        
                <form @submit.prevent="handleSubmit">
                <customInput v-model="email" :label="emailLabel"/> <!-- v-bind: je isto sto i :-->
                <customInput v-model="password" v-bind:label="passwordLabel"/> <!-- znaci custom input dobija label podatke od parenta a to je comp, jer su custom inputu potrebni -->
                <button>Log In</button>
    </form>


    </template>

    <script>
    import customInput from "../components/CustomInputComp.vue"
    export default {
    name: "comp",
    components: {customInput},
    data: function() {
        return {
            inputs: {
                'email',
                'password',
                'name'
            },
            email: "",
            password: "",
            title: "Login Form",
            emailLabel: 'Email',
            passwordLabel: 'Password'
};
    },
    methods: {
        handleSubmit() {
            console.log(this.email, this.password)
        }
    }
    }
        
    </script>


    <style>

    input {
        margin: 10px;
        color:  blue;
        display: block;
    }

    </style>
